{"tid":1773720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1212 如果有侮辱義士嘅人結婚你哋會點慶祝？","createTime":"2019-12-07T16:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T09:09:54.000Z","uid":343178,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb8071eb86fbfebb3756f54e2b375a43eb07029","tid":1773720,"uid":343178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"大家仲記得六月第一宗自殺新聞喺金鐘PP出現，有前少年警棍職員侮辱義士事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1227587\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1227587</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDghfJK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDghfJK.png&h=f63b11be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofK2OsH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofK2OsH.jpg&h=4cf111c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰日記住<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>過去賀佢<br />\n侮辱義士莫俊雄新婚之喜<br />\n全城去賀佢老母<br />\n日期：12月12日12點<br />\n地點：金鐘紅棉路婚姻註冊處<br />\n祝賀說話： <br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n出嚟呀自由閪<br />\n神秘號碼：70716977<br />\n個神秘號碼唔知咩嚟，不過應該可以打過去訂外賣嘅<br />\n記住大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span></span>祝佢去新屋嶺洞房"},{"pid":"a3e5b6966e7d33bbc6f70bdac072c172f3308a17","tid":1773720,"uid":343178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe137310907def1ac8d3710fddf7c9a7b866b32","tid":1773720,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"祝佢年年有今日，做1.1 同用吉儀做人情"},{"pid":"b183f95552a1909529226ee525063a5605af3d56","tid":1773720,"uid":343178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"10連推"},{"pid":"4846daa00cdaf0401f83e0c9f20343f5b3521776","tid":1773720,"uid":343178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"